[
  {
    "startTime": 4.14,
    "endTime": 4.3999999999999995,
    "text": "okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.63,
    "endTime": 56.650000000000006,
    "text": "He knows, You know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.74,
    "endTime": 58.080000000000005,
    "text": "He knows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.08,
    "endTime": 58.79,
    "text": "We broke into Gringotts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.79,
    "endTime": 60.339999999999996,
    "text": "He knows what we took."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.57,
    "endTime": 62.13,
    "text": "And he knows we're hunting Horcruxes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.94,
    "endTime": 65.66,
    "text": "You let him in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.34,
    "endTime": 66.77000000000001,
    "text": "Harry,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.77,
    "endTime": 68.07,
    "text": "you can't do that. Hermione."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.07,
    "endTime": 69.35,
    "text": "I can't always help it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.94,
    "endTime": 70.62,
    "text": "Maybe I can."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.62,
    "endTime": 71.24000000000001,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.27,
    "endTime": 71.91,
    "text": "Never mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.91,
    "endTime": 72.5,
    "text": "What happened?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.04,
    "endTime": 74.75,
    "text": "Well, he's angry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.33,
    "endTime": 76.28,
    "text": "And scared too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.74,
    "endTime": 79.77,
    "text": "He knows if we find and destroy all the Horcruxes will be able to kill him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.52,
    "endTime": 80.91,
    "text": "I reckon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.92,
    "endTime": 83.05,
    "text": "He'll stop at nothing to make sure we don't find the rest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.44,
    "endTime": 86.03,
    "text": "There's more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.33,
    "endTime": 87.39,
    "text": "One of them is at Hogwarts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.8,
    "endTime": 88.35,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.54,
    "endTime": 90.26,
    "text": "You saw it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.27,
    "endTime": 91.2,
    "text": "I saw at the castle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.36,
    "endTime": 92.2,
    "text": "And Rowena Ravenclaw."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.5,
    "endTime": 93.85,
    "text": "It must have something to do with her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.86,
    "endTime": 95.11,
    "text": "We have to go there now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.22,
    "endTime": 95.45,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.45,
    "endTime": 96.45,
    "text": "We can't do that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.04,
    "endTime": 97.94000000000001,
    "text": "We've got to plan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.94,
    "endTime": 98.75,
    "text": "Got to figure it out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.75,
    "endTime": 101.77,
    "text": "Hermione, any of our plans ever actually worked?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 102.5,
    "text": "We plan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.51,
    "endTime": 103.01,
    "text": "We get there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.02,
    "endTime": 105.92,
    "text": "All hell breaks loose is right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.0,
    "endTime": 110.85,
    "text": "One problem.  Save the Headmaster now, can't just walk through the front door."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.34,
    "endTime": 114.79,
    "text": "Um, well, we'll go to Hogsmeade."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.24,
    "endTime": 117.64999999999999,
    "text": "Take the secret passage in the cellar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.83,
    "endTime": 121.19,
    "text": "It's... There's something wrong with it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.38,
    "endTime": 128.75,
    "text": "It's like, you know, in the past, I've always been able to follow his thoughts, and now everything just feels disconnected."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.93,
    "endTime": 130.96,
    "text": "Maybe it's the whole crisis."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.38,
    "endTime": 133.03,
    "text": "Maybe he's going weak, and maybe he's dying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.37,
    "endTime": 136.05,
    "text": "No, no, it's It's more like he's wounded."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.84,
    "endTime": 138.38,
    "text": "If anything, he feels more dangerous."
  }
]